@TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:5178

### Test 1 — Login with seeded user
POST {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@taskflow.local",
  "password": "Demo@123"
}

### Create a task
POST {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Finish TaskFlow Day 3",
  "description": "Wire up the TasksController and verify CRUD works end to end.",
  "priority": 2,
  "dueDate": "2026-04-22T17:00:00Z"
}

### List all tasks
GET {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get one task (replace 1 with a real id)
GET {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a task — mark as completed
PUT {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Finish TaskFlow Day 3",
  "description": "Done!",
  "status": 2,
  "priority": 2,
  "dueDate": "2026-04-22T17:00:00Z"
}

### Delete a task
DELETE {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unauthorized test (no token) — expect 401
GET {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks